reviewText:
Excellent!!!! Thumb up! for those who want their kids fall in love with Spanish language.
Very animated/educational videos. Not boring at all. -->The only risk you'll have is to have your kids ask for them to play over and over again.... :)
My daughter watch this show everyday, she love it.
I would give it a 5-star review for content, but there seems to be so many repetitive songs between episodes.
